# Data Source

[Epicurious - Recipes with Rating and Nutrition | Kaggle](https://www.kaggle.com/hugodarwood/epirecipes)

While initially planning to utilise the CSV of this data, the JSON appears to have an easier format to understand w/ less hard coding required.
The Reasoning behind this, is that the csv has 600+ columns, while the JSON has a format which groups relevant information, such as tags and ingredients.



